query: SELECT AVG(dep_delay) FROM flights TABLESAMPLE SYSTEM(0.5) WHERE origin='ATL';
SELECT AVG(distance) FROM flights TABLESAMPLE SYSTEM(0.5) WHERE unique_carrier='TW';

SELECT year_date, COUNT(*) FROM flights TABLESAMPLE SYSTEM(0.5) WHERE origin_state_abr='LA' AND dest='JFK' GROUP BY year_date;
SELECT year_date, SUM(distance) FROM flights TABLESAMPLE SYSTEM(0.5) WHERE unique_carrier='9E' GROUP BY year_date;
SELECT origin_state_abr, SUM(air_time) FROM flights TABLESAMPLE SYSTEM(0.5) WHERE dest='HPN' GROUP BY origin_state_abr;
SELECT unique_carrier, AVG(dep_delay) FROM flights TABLESAMPLE SYSTEM(0.5) WHERE year_date=2005 AND origin='PHX' GROUP BY unique_carrier;
SELECT dest_state_abr, COUNT(*) FROM flights TABLESAMPLE SYSTEM(0.5) WHERE distance>2500 GROUP BY dest_state_abr;
SELECT unique_carrier, COUNT(*) FROM flights TABLESAMPLE SYSTEM(0.5) WHERE air_time>1000 AND dep_delay>1500 GROUP BY unique_carrier;
